**LibreOffice 7.6:**
- Introduced support for zoom gestures on touchpads.
- Added features like a new Page Number Wizard in Writer, improved paragraph style handling, and enhanced dictionary items of Hunspell and custom dictionaries.
- Improved font handling, especially for right-to-left scripts, CJK, and Asian alphabets.
